    CrumbTrail manages crumbs for a map item using a dedicated trackThread The intervalMillis is configurable and specifies how often to store crumbs in the CrumbDatabase Crumbs are only stored if the map item has moved by distThreshold Crumbs are sent to the UI no more than once every 2 seconds
